'''莉迪亚·苏珊娜·亨特'''（{{lang-en|Lydia Susanna Hunter}}，{{bd|1945年|4月2日||}}），艺名'''琳达·亨特'''（{{lang|en|Linda Hunt}}）是一位[[美国电影|美国电影]]、[[电视|电视]]及[[舞台剧|舞台剧]]女[[演员|演员]]，因為於1982年的[[澳大利亚电影|澳大利亚电影]]《[[危险年代|危险年代]]》中反串出演一位名為Billy Kwan的男摄影师<ref name=IMDb>{{cite web | title = Linda Hunt | work = [[IMDb|IMDb]] | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001373/ | access-date = 2013-04-07 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308064429/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001373/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>而获得[[第56届学院奖|第56届奥斯卡金像奖]][[学院奖最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角奖]]，成为奥斯卡奖历史上首位因反串出演一个不同性别的角色而获奖的演员<ref name= "Worrell">{{cite news | last1 = Worrell | first1 = Denise | first2 = Gerald | last2 = Clarke | title = The Night off the Great Prom | work = 《[[时代周刊|时代]]》周刊 | pages =  | language =  | publisher =  | date = 1984年4月23日 | url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,921697,00.html | accessdate = 2013年4月7日 | archive-date = 2013年8月22日 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130822161429/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,921697,00.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，此外这一角色还为她赢得了{{link-en|澳大利亚电影协会最佳女配角奖|Australian Film Institute Award for Best Actress in a Supporting Role}}及第41届[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳电影女配角奖提名<ref name=IMDbAwards>{{cite web | title = Linda Hunt – Awards | work = IMDb | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001373/awards | access-date = 2013-04-07 | archive-date = 2017-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312010428/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001373/awards | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==早年生活==
1945年4月2日亨特出生于新泽西州的[[莫里斯敦_(新澤西州)|莫里斯敦]]。她的父亲是Harper Fuel Oil的副总裁。她的母亲是一名钢琴教师，曾在韦斯特波特音乐学院任教，并在康涅狄格州[[韦斯特波特_(康涅狄格州)|韦斯特波特]]的Saugatuck公理会合唱团演出，亨特在那里长大。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Linda Hunt Biography |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/6/Linda-Hunt.html |work=filmreference.com |accessdate=2010-12-12 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807111642/http://www.filmreference.com/film/6/Linda-Hunt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>她有一个姐姐。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Family for Linda Hunt |url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/90862%7C0/Linda-Hunt/family.html |work=Turner Classic Movies |accessdate=2017-12-18 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803064430/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/90862%7C0/Linda-Hunt/family.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>亨特就读于{{tsl|en|Interlochen Arts Academy||Interlochen艺术学院}}<ref name=IAAarchives>{{cite web|last=Hanson|first=Byron|title=From the Archives with Byron Hanson: February 2010|url=http://www.interlochen.org/crescendo/archives-byron-hanson-february-2010|work=Interlochen Center for the Arts|accessdate=2011-07-03|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602175312/http://www.interlochen.org/crescendo/archives-byron-hanson-february-2010|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和伊利诺伊州[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的{{tsl|en|Goodman School of Drama||古德曼戏剧学院}}，这个学院现在是[[德保罗大学|德保罗大学]]的一部分。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lacob |first=Jace |date=2011-09-26 |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2011/09/26/linda-hunt-on-ncis-la-hetty-lange-year-of-living-dangerously.html |title=The Cult of Linda Hunt |work=The Daily Beast |accessdate=2011-11-03 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215073401/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2011/09/26/linda-hunt-on-ncis-la-hetty-lange-year-of-living-dangerously.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=DePaul>{{cite web|title=The Theatre School: History |url=http://theatreschool.depaul.edu/about_history.php |work=DePaul University |accessdate=2011-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719191243/http://theatreschool.depaul.edu/about_history.php |archivedate=2011-07-19 }}</ref>

